div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wuy1665702640384.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wuy1665702640384.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wuy1665702640384.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wuy1665702640384\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      trigger onTabButton\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wuy1665702640384__trigger_ontabbutton_396933\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">onTabButton</span> trigger is used to implement the processing that should occur when a user clicks the tab button in the active tab.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wuy1665702640384__topic_d117713e1_d117714e1_d117715e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104wuy1665702640384_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"wuy1665702640384__codeblock_ask_hbh_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger onTabButton\n; enter your code here\n    \nend ; trigger onTabButton\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"wuy1665702640384__section_w231ab1b7b5_w232ab1b7_w233ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wuy1665702640384__table_d14588e1_d14589e1_d14590e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Applies to:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Form widgets: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activation:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activated when the user clicks the tab button on a tab.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Default behavior:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Behavior upon completion:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wuy1665702640384__topic_d83757e1_d83758e1_d83759e1_d83760e1_d83761e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d301230e134\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wuy1665702640384__p_d117719e1_d117720e1_d117721e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">onTabButton</span> trigger is typically used to close the active tab when the user clicks on the tab button. This button is displayed only if the TabButton property of the TabEx widget is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wuy1665702640384__topic_d83762e1_d83763e1_d83764e1_d83765e1_d83766e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d301230e149\">\n                       \n Applies To\n </h2>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ish1665702640453.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tab Button ( button)</a><p>Determines whether the active tab displays a button, such as a Close button, that executes the onTabButton extended trigger when clicked. True or False (default).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611087\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611087\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "trigger onTabButton Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 trigger onTabButton The onTabButton trigger is used to implement the processing that should occur when a user clicks the tab button in the active tab. Explain this code trigger onTabButton ; enter your code here end ; trigger onTabButton\" Copy Applies to: Form widgets: utabex (TabEx) Activation: Activated when the user clicks the tab button on a tab. Default behavior: None Behavior upon completion: None Description The onTabButton trigger is typically used to close the active tab when the user clicks on the tab button. This button is displayed only if the TabButton property of the TabEx widget is True . Applies To Related Links Tab Button ( button) Determines whether the active tab displays a button, such as a Close button, that executes the onTabButton extended trigger when clicked. True or False (default). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}